'''馬克薩斯水雞''' ([[學名|學名]]：''Porphyrio paepae'') 是一種已滅絕的[[秧雞|秧雞]]，分布於[[馬克薩斯群島|馬克薩斯群島]]的[[希瓦瓦島|希瓦瓦島]]和[[塔瓦塔島|塔瓦塔島]]。 本種於1988年發表描述，基於600年前的[[亞化石|亞化石]]，但他們可能生存到約1900年代。在[[保羅·高更|保羅·高更]]1902年的作品《Le Sorcier d'Hiva Oa ou le Marquisien à la cape rouge》右下角出現的鳥，可能就是馬克薩斯水雞。<ref>''«[…] '''d’'''Hiva Oa […]»'' as such, is pronounced /diˈva oˈa/, while the Polynesian '''h''' is always a /ɦ/: this shows Gauguin had a very poor knowledge of the Polynesian languages. He should have written '''''de''' Hiva Oa''. Despite Polynesian inscriptions, often approximative, Gauguin seems to have been unable to speak any Polynesian languages, as it is said locally.{{Citation needed|date=February 2012}}</ref> 而[[索爾·海爾達|索爾·海爾達]]在1937年聲稱在[[希瓦瓦島|希瓦瓦島]]上見過類似的鳥類。<ref name="Extinct Birds">{{cite book
